com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.os
Interface AIXLocalUser

All Superinterfaces:
com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.Capability, com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.DeployModelObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, User
All Known Implementing Classes:
AIXLocalUserImpl
public interface AIXLocalUser
extends User

A representation of the model object 'AIX Local User'.

The following features are supported:

  • Account Description
  • Account Disabled
  • Account Expiration Time
  • Change Password Next Logon
  • Full Name
  • Home Dir
  • Is Admin
  • Login Permitted
  • Login Retries
  • Login Times
  • Max Char Repeats
  • Max Password Age In Weeks
  • Max Password Valid Weeks
  • Min Alpha Chars In Password
  • Min Diff Chars
  • Min Other Chars In Password
  • Min Password Age In Weeks
  • Min Password Length
  • Not Reusable Number Of Passwords
  • Pass Reuse Not Allowed In Weeks
  • Password Change Warn Time
  • Password Never Expires
  • Primary Auth Method
  • Remote Login Is Allowed
  • Secondary Auth Method
  • Shell
  • Su Groups Allowed
  • Su Is Allowed
  • Time Last Login
  • User Cannot Change Password
  • User Name
  • User Registering Method
  • User Sid
  • Usuccessful Login Count

See Also:
OsPackage.getAIXLocalUser()
